    SELECT p."Id", p."CreatedDate", p."Name", p."Price", p."Stock", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    WHERE p."Id" = @__Parse_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId", f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS f0 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = f0."Id"
) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"
ORDER BY p1."Id", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"

FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."CreatedDate", p."Name", p."Price", p."Stock", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    WHERE p."Id" = @__Parse_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId", f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS f0 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = f0."Id"
) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"
ORDER BY p1."Id", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"

    LIMIT 1
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId", f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail"

FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."CreatedDate", p."Name", p."Price", p."Properties", p."Stock", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    WHERE p."Id" = @__Parse_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId", f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS f0 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = f0."Id"
) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"
ORDER BY p1."Id", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"

2024-04-05 15:22:46.789 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (116ms) [Parameters=[@__Parse_0='?' (DbType = Guid)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."Id", p1."CreatedDate", p1."Name", p1."Price", p1."Properties", p1."Stock", p1."UpdatedDate", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."CreatedDate", p."Name", p."Price", p."Properties", p."Stock", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    WHERE p."Id" = @__Parse_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId", f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS f0 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = f0."Id"
) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"
ORDER BY p1."Id", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"

    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId"

SELECT p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."Stock", p1."Price", p1."CreatedDate", p1."UpdatedDate", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"

    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"

    ) AS f0 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = f0."Id"
) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"

SELECT p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."Stock", p1."Price", p1."CreatedDate", p1."UpdatedDate", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS f0 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = f0."Id"
) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"
ORDER BY p1."Id", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"

SELECT p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."Stock", p1."Price", p1."CreatedDate", p1."UpdatedDate", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS f0 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = f0."Id"
) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"
ORDER BY p1."Id", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"

SELECT p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."Stock", p1."Price", p1."CreatedDate", p1."UpdatedDate", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS f0 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = f0."Id"
) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"
ORDER BY p1."Id", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"

SELECT p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."Stock", p1."Price", p1."CreatedDate", p1."UpdatedDate", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS f0 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = f0."Id"
) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"
ORDER BY p1."Id", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"

SELECT p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."Stock", p1."Price", p1."CreatedDate", p1."UpdatedDate", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS f0 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = f0."Id"
) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"
ORDER BY p1."Id", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"

SELECT p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."Stock", p1."Price", p1."CreatedDate", p1."UpdatedDate", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS f0 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = f0."Id"
) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"

    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId"

    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (

    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"

    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"

    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_0 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId"

SELECT p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."Stock", p1."Price", p1."CreatedDate", p1."UpdatedDate", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS f0 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = f0."Id"
) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"
ORDER BY p1."Id", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"

SELECT count(*)::int

2024-04-05 16:49:31.013 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (16ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."Stock", p1."Price", p1."CreatedDate", p1."UpdatedDate", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS f0 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = f0."Id"
) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"
ORDER BY p1."Id", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"

SELECT p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."Stock", p1."Price", p1."CreatedDate", p1."UpdatedDate", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS f0 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = f0."Id"
) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"

    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1

2024-04-05 17:03:38.087 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (38ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT count(*)::int
FROM "Products" AS p
2024-04-05 17:03:38.128 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (22ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."Stock", p1."Price", p1."CreatedDate", p1."UpdatedDate", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS f0 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = f0."Id"
) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"
ORDER BY p1."Id", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"

2024-04-05 17:04:53.991 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (4ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."Stock", p1."Price", p1."CreatedDate", p1."UpdatedDate", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS f0 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = f0."Id"
) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"
ORDER BY p1."Id", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"

) AS p1

SELECT count(*)::int
FROM "Products" AS p
2024-04-05 17:12:07.594 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."Stock", p1."Price", p1."CreatedDate", p1."UpdatedDate", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS f0 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = f0."Id"
) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"
ORDER BY p1."Id", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"

SELECT p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."Stock", p1."Price", p1."CreatedDate", p1."UpdatedDate", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS f0 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = f0."Id"
) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"
ORDER BY p1."Id", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"

2024-04-05 17:29:39.525 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (5ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT count(*)::int
FROM "Products" AS p
2024-04-05 17:29:39.546 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (4ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."Stock", p1."Price", p1."CreatedDate", p1."UpdatedDate", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS f0 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = f0."Id"
) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"
ORDER BY p1."Id", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"

2024-04-05 17:29:46.713 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."Stock", p1."Price", p1."CreatedDate", p1."UpdatedDate", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS f0 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = f0."Id"
) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"
ORDER BY p1."Id", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"

2024-04-05 17:30:38.479 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (7ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT count(*)::int
FROM "Products" AS p
2024-04-05 17:30:38.483 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (3ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."Stock", p1."Price", p1."CreatedDate", p1."UpdatedDate", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS f0 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = f0."Id"
) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"
ORDER BY p1."Id", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"

2024-04-05 17:48:19.016 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (7ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."Stock", p1."Price", p1."CreatedDate", p1."UpdatedDate", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS f0 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = f0."Id"
) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"
ORDER BY p1."Id", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"

    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1

2024-04-05 17:51:04.018 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT count(*)::int
FROM "Products" AS p
2024-04-05 17:51:04.023 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (3ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."Stock", p1."Price", p1."CreatedDate", p1."UpdatedDate", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS f0 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = f0."Id"
) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"
ORDER BY p1."Id", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"

SELECT p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."Stock", p1."Price", p1."CreatedDate", p1."UpdatedDate", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS f0 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = f0."Id"
) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"

2024-04-05 17:52:31.164 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."Stock", p1."Price", p1."CreatedDate", p1."UpdatedDate", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS f0 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = f0."Id"
) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"
ORDER BY p1."Id", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"

    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1

SELECT count(*)::int
FROM "Products" AS p
2024-04-05 17:53:18.376 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (26ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."Stock", p1."Price", p1."CreatedDate", p1."UpdatedDate", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS f0 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = f0."Id"
) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"
ORDER BY p1."Id", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"

SELECT p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."Stock", p1."Price", p1."CreatedDate", p1."UpdatedDate", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS f0 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = f0."Id"
) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"
ORDER BY p1."Id", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"

2024-04-05 18:02:21.763 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (42ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT count(*)::int
FROM "Products" AS p
2024-04-05 18:02:21.788 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (11ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."Stock", p1."Price", p1."CreatedDate", p1."UpdatedDate", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS f0 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = f0."Id"
) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"
ORDER BY p1."Id", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"

SELECT count(*)::int
FROM "Products" AS p
2024-04-05 18:03:10.333 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (3ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."Stock", p1."Price", p1."CreatedDate", p1."UpdatedDate", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS f0 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = f0."Id"
) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"
ORDER BY p1."Id", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"

SELECT p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."Stock", p1."Price", p1."CreatedDate", p1."UpdatedDate", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"

) AS p1

2024-04-05 18:12:03.418 +03:00 [INF] Executing action method UlukunShopAPI.API.Controllers.ProductsController.Get (UlukunShopAPI.API) - Validation state: "Valid"
2024-04-05 18:12:03.505 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (15ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT count(*)::int
FROM "Products" AS p
2024-04-05 18:12:03.543 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (4ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."Stock", p1."Price", p1."CreatedDate", p1."UpdatedDate", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS f0 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = f0."Id"
) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"
ORDER BY p1."Id", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"

2024-04-05 18:12:09.384 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (1ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."Stock", p1."Price", p1."CreatedDate", p1."UpdatedDate", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS f0 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = f0."Id"
) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"
ORDER BY p1."Id", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"

SELECT p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."Stock", p1."Price", p1."CreatedDate", p1."UpdatedDate", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"
        FROM "Files" AS f

2024-04-05 18:16:41.843 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (10ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."Stock", p1."Price", p1."CreatedDate", p1."UpdatedDate", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS f0 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = f0."Id"
) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"
ORDER BY p1."Id", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"

2024-04-05 18:17:16.939 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (1ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."Stock", p1."Price", p1."CreatedDate", p1."UpdatedDate", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS f0 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = f0."Id"
) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"
ORDER BY p1."Id", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"

SELECT p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."Stock", p1."Price", p1."CreatedDate", p1."UpdatedDate", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS f0 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = f0."Id"
) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"
ORDER BY p1."Id", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"

2024-04-05 18:22:37.184 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (1ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."Stock", p1."Price", p1."CreatedDate", p1."UpdatedDate", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS f0 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = f0."Id"
) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"
ORDER BY p1."Id", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"

2024-04-05 18:24:12.997 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (6ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."Stock", p1."Price", p1."CreatedDate", p1."UpdatedDate", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS f0 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = f0."Id"
) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"
ORDER BY p1."Id", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"

SELECT p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."Stock", p1."Price", p1."CreatedDate", p1."UpdatedDate", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"

        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'

) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"

SELECT p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."Stock", p1."Price", p1."CreatedDate", p1."UpdatedDate", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (

SELECT count(*)::int
FROM "Products" AS p
2024-04-05 18:31:49.113 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (9ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."Stock", p1."Price", p1."CreatedDate", p1."UpdatedDate", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS f0 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = f0."Id"
) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"
ORDER BY p1."Id", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"

2024-04-05 18:34:05.407 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (9ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."Stock", p1."Price", p1."CreatedDate", p1."UpdatedDate", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS f0 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = f0."Id"
) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"
ORDER BY p1."Id", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"

SELECT p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."Stock", p1."Price", p1."CreatedDate", p1."UpdatedDate", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"

) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"

) AS p1

2024-04-05 18:36:42.497 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT count(*)::int
FROM "Products" AS p
2024-04-05 18:36:42.513 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."Stock", p1."Price", p1."CreatedDate", p1."UpdatedDate", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS f0 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = f0."Id"
) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"
ORDER BY p1."Id", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"

SELECT p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."Stock", p1."Price", p1."CreatedDate", p1."UpdatedDate", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS f0 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = f0."Id"
) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"
ORDER BY p1."Id", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"

    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_0 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId"

2024-04-05 18:37:34.398 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (9ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."Stock", p1."Price", p1."CreatedDate", p1."UpdatedDate", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS f0 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = f0."Id"
) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"
ORDER BY p1."Id", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"

    LIMIT @__p_0 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1

    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0

SELECT p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."Stock", p1."Price", p1."CreatedDate", p1."UpdatedDate", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS f0 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = f0."Id"
) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"

SELECT p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."Stock", p1."Price", p1."CreatedDate", p1."UpdatedDate", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS f0 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = f0."Id"
) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"
ORDER BY p1."Id", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"

FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (

SELECT count(*)::int

2024-04-05 18:48:15.778 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (20ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."Stock", p1."Price", p1."CreatedDate", p1."UpdatedDate", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS f0 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = f0."Id"
) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"
ORDER BY p1."Id", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"

2024-04-05 18:59:04.075 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (14ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."Stock", p1."Price", p1."CreatedDate", p1."UpdatedDate", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS f0 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = f0."Id"
) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"
ORDER BY p1."Id", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"

2024-04-05 18:59:49.697 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT count(*)::int
FROM "Products" AS p
2024-04-05 18:59:49.705 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (5ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."Stock", p1."Price", p1."CreatedDate", p1."UpdatedDate", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS f0 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = f0."Id"
) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"
ORDER BY p1."Id", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"

2024-04-05 19:00:48.218 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."Stock", p1."Price", p1."CreatedDate", p1."UpdatedDate", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS f0 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = f0."Id"
) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"
ORDER BY p1."Id", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"

SELECT count(*)::int
FROM "Products" AS p
2024-04-05 19:02:18.397 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (12ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."Stock", p1."Price", p1."CreatedDate", p1."UpdatedDate", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS f0 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = f0."Id"
) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"
ORDER BY p1."Id", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"

SELECT count(*)::int
FROM "Products" AS p
2024-04-05 19:03:50.499 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (34ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."Stock", p1."Price", p1."CreatedDate", p1."UpdatedDate", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImageFilesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS f0 ON p0."ProductImageFilesId" = f0."Id"
) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"
ORDER BY p1."Id", s."ProductImageFilesId", s."ProductsId"

    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImagesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS f0 ON p0."ProductImagesId" = f0."Id"
) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"
ORDER BY p1."Id", s."ProductImagesId", s."ProductsId"

2024-04-05 19:10:22.592 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (5ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."Stock", p1."Price", p1."CreatedDate", p1."UpdatedDate", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail", s."ProductImagesId", s."ProductsId"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImagesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS f0 ON p0."ProductImagesId" = f0."Id"
) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"
ORDER BY p1."Id", s."ProductImagesId", s."ProductsId"

2024-04-05 19:10:59.252 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (8ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."Stock", p1."Price", p1."CreatedDate", p1."UpdatedDate", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail", s."ProductImagesId", s."ProductsId"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImagesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS f0 ON p0."ProductImagesId" = f0."Id"
) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"
ORDER BY p1."Id", s."ProductImagesId", s."ProductsId"

SELECT p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."Stock", p1."Price", p1."CreatedDate", p1."UpdatedDate", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail", s."ProductImagesId", s."ProductsId"

    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImagesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"

) AS p1

SELECT count(*)::int
FROM "Products" AS p
2024-04-05 19:18:29.847 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (1ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."Stock", p1."Price", p1."CreatedDate", p1."UpdatedDate", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail", s."ProductImagesId", s."ProductsId"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImagesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS f0 ON p0."ProductImagesId" = f0."Id"
) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"
ORDER BY p1."Id", s."ProductImagesId", s."ProductsId"

FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImagesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"
        FROM "Files" AS f

    ) AS f0 ON p0."ProductImagesId" = f0."Id"
) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"

2024-04-05 19:23:04.034 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (10ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."Stock", p1."Price", p1."CreatedDate", p1."UpdatedDate", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail", s."ProductImagesId", s."ProductsId"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImagesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS f0 ON p0."ProductImagesId" = f0."Id"
) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"
ORDER BY p1."Id", s."ProductImagesId", s."ProductsId"

    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImagesId", p0."ProductsId"

SELECT count(*)::int
FROM "Products" AS p
2024-04-05 19:26:08.236 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (1ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."Stock", p1."Price", p1."CreatedDate", p1."UpdatedDate", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail", s."ProductImagesId", s."ProductsId"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImagesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS f0 ON p0."ProductImagesId" = f0."Id"
) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"
ORDER BY p1."Id", s."ProductImagesId", s."ProductsId"

SELECT p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."Stock", p1."Price", p1."CreatedDate", p1."UpdatedDate", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail", s."ProductImagesId", s."ProductsId"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImagesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"

        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS f0 ON p0."ProductImagesId" = f0."Id"
) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"

2024-04-05 19:31:32.358 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (8ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."Stock", p1."Price", p1."CreatedDate", p1."UpdatedDate", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail", s."ProductImagesId", s."ProductsId"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImagesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS f0 ON p0."ProductImagesId" = f0."Id"
) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"
ORDER BY p1."Id", s."ProductImagesId", s."ProductsId"

2024-04-05 19:31:38.330 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."Stock", p1."Price", p1."CreatedDate", p1."UpdatedDate", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail", s."ProductImagesId", s."ProductsId"
FROM (
    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImagesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"
        FROM "Files" AS f
        WHERE f."Discriminator" = 'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS f0 ON p0."ProductImagesId" = f0."Id"
) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"
ORDER BY p1."Id", s."ProductImagesId", s."ProductsId"

SELECT p1."Id", p1."Name", p1."Stock", p1."Price", p1."CreatedDate", p1."UpdatedDate", s."Id", s."CreatedDate", s."Discriminator", s."FileName", s."Path", s."Storage", s."isThumbnail", s."ProductImagesId", s."ProductsId"

    SELECT p."Id", p."Name", p."Stock", p."Price", p."CreatedDate", p."UpdatedDate"
    FROM "Products" AS p
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS p1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f0."Id", f0."CreatedDate", f0."Discriminator", f0."FileName", f0."Path", f0."Storage", f0."isThumbnail", p0."ProductImagesId", p0."ProductsId"
    FROM "ProductProductImageFile" AS p0
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT f."Id", f."CreatedDate", f."Discriminator", f."FileName", f."Path", f."Storage", f."isThumbnail"

) AS s ON p1."Id" = s."ProductsId"
